跣親。<br />\n<br />\nB連同中立嘅C去指責A整污糟地下跣親C？<br />\n甚至A自己都覺得自己有責任，要對C道歉？"},{"pid":"aea5ddc91bd23228e812d9c41340e3629c97c8d5","tid":1473173,"uid":41796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b7aa4a664a902f63c5beffd2e047b9c0255ac8c","tid":1473173,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68716657_10157949422747448_2988651068776251392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_eui2=AeEEI2_PMoj6df2wBGimS1HrEA5R7lYcW4ZY_iEVNMOU7tXkp3gUDxWp9ELEkHy7aTqOg51JBoUhhV47FRuJqKc-fGuzQKXM3xznhkq8ZjzAoA&amp;_nc_oc=AQnORQ2VwEJEWi1hdiyZ0Krtr-vuIdrmFGqWbt3Qfl6_EI81-S6sCMGFvSLkkKX2CPY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=f352a9183e5c671cbf585c73ec1cb226&amp;oe=5DD2E715\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68716657_10157949422747448_2988651068776251392_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_eui2%3DAeEEI2_PMoj6df2wBGimS1HrEA5R7lYcW4ZY_iEVNMOU7tXkp3gUDxWp9ELEkHy7aTqOg51JBoUhhV47FRuJqKc-fGuzQKXM3xznhkq8ZjzAoA%26_nc_oc%3DAQnORQ2VwEJEWi1hdiyZ0Krtr-vuIdrmFGqWbt3Qfl6_EI81-S6sCMGFvSLkkKX2CPY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Df352a9183e5c671cbf585c73ec1cb226%26oe%3D5DD2E715&h=77ec375f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:30:35.000Z","msg":"串錯字<br />\ninco<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">n</span>venience<br />\n純粹善意提醒<br />\n絕無他意"}]}